data.description: This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, spanning 1,984 square feet and constructed in 2000, boasts two living areas and has undergone a complete revitalization with fresh paint and new flooring. Situated on a 5-acre lot enveloped by trees, the property includes a generous 30x50 workshop with an added 12-foot lean-to and an extra single-car garage. This residence offers privacy and tranquility, surrounded by lush greenery, a substantial yard, well-landscaped gardens, and a variety of fruit trees.
